title: THE GLEN CAMPBELL GOODTIME HOUR -- with John Wayne, The Monkees
description:
This 1969 First Season show also has singer Jeannie C Riley and a cameo appearance by Joey Bishop.

Since this is from You Tube and The Monkees' pre-recorded ( lip-synched ) number was muted, I managed to find a clip of that -- also from You Tube , which somehow avoided copyright infringement after 2 years ! You'll find it here in the torrent
